{"timestamp": "2025-12-04 16:05:06.227322", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission completed.\n\n- Is anomaly: true\n- Faulty devices: vpn_server_1\n- Root cause: host_vpn_membership_missing\n\nRationale:\n- vpn_server_1’s WireGuard configuration lacks a peer entry for host_1 (172.16.1.11), preventing a handshake and blocking overlay access to 172.16.1.21/22.\n- Underlay routing is healthy.\n- Additionally observed policy issue: web_server_1_1 and web_server_1_2 are reachable directly over 20.0.0.0/24, violating the “VPN-only” requirement.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2338, "output_tokens": 130, "total_tokens": 2468, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 2176}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
